==Documentation==
This template creates the individual company cards that show on the Chracters page. The data is passed into this template from Module:CompanyQuery

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Title || The original game name / path in wiki
|-
|| CleanTitle || The name with Games/ removed
|-
|| Developed || Developed X Games
|-
|| Published || Published X Games
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
|| Image || Thumbnail image in raw format
|}

===Usage===
